title: Making strides against breast cancer
text:
Making strides against breast cancer 0 comments 
Making Strides Against Breast Cancer is a celebration of survivorship - an occasion to express hope and our shared determination to make this breast cancer's last century. 
You can help finish the fight against breast cancer by raising funds for and walking with American Cancer Society Making Strides of Harrisburg on October 17, 2015 on City Island in Harrisburg. Join more than one million people, nationwide, each year, who are helping to end breast cancer.
